               <msContents class="#MTM">
                  <summary><p>A multiple-text manuscript containing three works, notably in praise of Gaṇeśa:
  <list rend="numbered">
  <item><title xml:lang="ta">Piḷḷaiyār Akaval</title> 1, that is, <title xml:lang="ta">Vināyakar Akaval</title> attributed to Auvaiyār (Zvelebil 1995, p. 770).</item>
    <item><title xml:lang="ta">Piḷḷaiyār Akaval</title> 2.</item>
    <item><title xml:lang="ta">Iraṭṭai Maṇimālai</title>, that is, <title xml:lang="ta">Mayilaviraṭṭai Maṇimālai</title>. In 21 stanzas: the <foreign xml:lang="ta">kāppu</foreign> + 20 numbered stanzas.</item>
  </list>
</p>
    </summary>
                  
